japan februari current account , trade surplu jump japan 's current account surplu rose to 7.38 billion dlr in februari from 3.89 billion a year ago and from 4.95 billion in januari , the financ ministri said . the trade surplu rose to 8.14 billion dlr in februari from 4.77 billion a year earlier and 5.70 billion in januari . the long-term capit account deficit widen to 11.40 billion dlr from 8.06 billion a year ago , but it narrow from 12.32 billion in januari , the ministri said . japan 's februari export rose to 16.74 billion dlr from 14.89 billion in februari 1986 and from 14.65 billion in januari , the ministri said . import fell to 8.61 billion from 10.12 billion a year earlier and 8.94 billion in januari . the invis trade deficit fell to 617 mln dlr in februari from 693 mln a year earlier , but wa up from a 527 mln deficit in januari . figur do not talli exactli becaus of round . transfer payment narrow to a 140 mln dlr deficit last month from a 185 mln deficit a year earlier and a 225 mln deficit in januari . the basic balanc of payment deficit in februari fell to 4.02 billion dlr from 4.17 billion in februari 1986 and 7.37 billion in januari . short-term capit account payment swung to a 1.28 billion dlr deficit in februari from a 1.60 billion surplu a year earlier and a 1.44 billion dlr surplu in januari . error and omiss were 2.65 billion dlr in surplu , compar with a 1.27 billion surplu a year earlier and a 1.10 billion deficit in januari . the overal balanc of payment deficit rose to 2.65 billion dlr from 1.30 billion a year earlier but wa down from 7.04 billion in januari .